--------------------------------------------------Solving Sylvester Equations----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Developed by: Hari Shrawgi

Language: MATLAB

--------------------------------------------------Solving Sylvester Equations----------------------------------------------------------------------------

The scripts together constitute two methods to solve Sylvester Equation.
First method uses Kronecker product to convert the equation into a vectorized linear equation, which is then solved substitution.
Second method uses Schur factorization instead.

Following are descriptions of the various scripts:

1. sylvester_kronecker.m: Implementation of the first method to solve Sylvester equation using Kronecker product.
2. QRapp1_modifed.m: Finds Schur decomposition using QR algorithm with Householder reflections.
3. sylvester_schur.m: Implementation of the second method to solve Sylvester equation using Schur factorizaion.

Rest of the scripts are helper scripts.

